{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the sole survivor of a shipwreck in the 17th century, you must quickly learn to adapt and survive on a mysterious and ruthless island filled with deadly threats and secrets to explore. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/BSI_Realistic_survival.gif?t=1737471549\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A ruthless roguelike experience with short intense sessions. No hand-holding, survive as best you can; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Progression system. Surviving longer, unlocks new resources and improves further chances;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Randomized resources and consequence-based outcomes to your decisions. Every player will have their unique experience; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dynamic open world game featuring realistic, simulated physics and systems-based gameplay. Day and night, fire, liquid, etc., all with a direct impact on gameplay;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A captivating narrative, set in a 17th century storybook atmosphere. The story changes according to the player`s progress and decisions.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/BSI_Intense_Roguelike.gif?t=1737471549\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bootstrap Island is the most realistic survival adventure you can experience without putting your life in danger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Co-funded by the European Union. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/Kaasrahastanud_EL_kaksiklogod_ENG_hor_white__2_.png?t=1737471549\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Co-funded by European Union Creative Europe Media.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=